metadata.name: Alternate Dimension
metadata.description:
Have you ever wondered what else could be out there. I feel at least once in our lives most of us or all of us have.

This collection explores my dreams, my imagination and my outer limits.

I came up with this idea and collection from a dream I recently had thinking about my past, present and soon to be future.

We all want to feel connected to something for myself it mostly the Earth.

As humans we give off loads of energy each and everyday, if you could listen to it what do you think it would say??

This piece is a part of my energy connecting with Earth, having conversations about what comes next..

I wanted to invoke a feeling, a presence with this piece.
